10:16.549 --> 10:18.418
HUSBAND OF 43 YEARS, BEN WALD,

10:18.418 --> 10:19.786
DISCOVERED AN EARLIER BOUT OF

10:19.786 --> 10:20.987
CANCER HAD RETURNED, SOON AFTER,

10:20.987 --> 10:22.255
THE DISEASE BEGAN TAKING A

10:22.255 --> 10:23.690
LETHAL TOLL.

