>> BEN WOKE ME UP IN THE MIDDLE

10:35.235 --> 10:38.471
OF THE NIGHT AND HE SAID, PAM,

10:38.471 --> 10:43.209
WE GOTTA TALK.

10:43.209 --> 10:44.644
I DON'T WANT TO KEEP, YOU KNOW,

10:44.644 --> 10:49.749
I'M DYING, PAM.

