I'VE HAD A GOOD LIFE WITH YOU

10:50.950 --> 10:54.153
AND BONNIE.

10:54.153 --> 10:58.157
I REALLY DON'T WANT TO JUST KEEP

10:58.157 --> 10:59.425
LIVING LIKE THIS.

