I WANT TO EXPLORE OREGON'S DEATH

11:00.860 --> 11:06.199
WITH DIGNITY LAW.

11:06.199 --> 11:07.567
>> Reporter: UNDER OREGON'S LAW,

11:07.567 --> 11:09.168
A DOCTOR MUST DETERMINE A

11:09.168 --> 11:10.203
TERMINALLY ILL PATIENT HAS SIX

11:10.203 --> 11:10.970
MONTHS OR FEWER TO LIVE.

11:10.970 --> 11:12.005
THE PHYSICIAN CAN WRITE A LIFE

11:12.005 --> 11:13.740
ENDING PRESCRIPTION ONLY AFTER A

11:13.740 --> 11:15.141
SECOND DOCTOR SIGNS ON AND BOTH

11:15.141 --> 11:16.142
AGREE THE PATIENT IS OF SOUND

11:16.142 --> 11:17.343
MIND.

11:17.343 --> 11:18.511
THE PATIENT MUST REQUEST THE

11:18.511 --> 11:20.046
DRUG AGAIN 15 DAYS AFTER THE

11:20.046 --> 11:23.616
INITIAL REQUEST.

11:23.616 --> 11:25.652
BUT ONCE THE PATIENT HAS IT, THE

11:25.652 --> 11:27.854
DOCTORS' ROLE IS OVER.

11:27.854 --> 11:33.726
SINCE THE LAW WENT INTO EFFECT

11:33.726 --> 11:34.794
IN 1997, NEARLY 1,200 PEOPLE

11:34.794 --> 11:38.464
HAVE RECEIVED LIFE-ENDING

11:38.464 --> 11:39.666
PRESCRIPTIONS, BUT JUST 752 HAVE

11:39.666 --> 11:41.167
ACTUALLY TAKEN THEM AND DIED.

11:41.167 --> 11:43.403
OTHERS DIED SOONER AND SOME

11:43.403 --> 11:45.605
CHANGED THEIR MINDS.

11:45.605 --> 11:46.506
AS BEN'S HEALTH DETERIORATED, HE

11:46.506 --> 11:47.440
AND PAM SOUGHT HELP FROM

11:47.440 --> 11:48.575
COMPASSION AND CHOICES, THE

11:48.575 --> 11:49.742
GROUP SUPPORTING BRITTANY

11:49.742 --> 11:50.577
MAYNARD.

